INSTALLATION
============
Please see Getting Started section here: http://code.google.com/p/approcket/

RELEASE NOTES
=============

Version 2.0.0 - December 1, 2009
--------------------------------
  -	Separate thread per each entity - now different entities are replicated parallel, not in a row
  - SEND_FIELDS_EXCLUDE configuration option 
  - Bunch of bug-fixes


Version 1.2.0 - December 17, 2008
---------------------------------
  - Fixed sending of lists
  - Added support for embedded string lists (list that are stored in a single MySQL TEXT column as values separated by '|')


Version 1.1.0 - December 14, 2008
---------------------------------
  - Fixed boolean value handling
  - Added example
  - Secured rocket URL via secret key exchange
  - Added MySQL database engine configuration parameter
  - Implemented BLOB support


Version 1.0.1 - December 8, 2008
---------------------------------
  - Fixed logging for daemon mode (station.py -d)
  - Improved logging for erroneous responses


Version 1.0.0 - November 22, 2008
---------------------------------
  - First release version